  <brief_title>Effect of Vitamin D Replacement During Winter Months in Patients With Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Cholecalciferol on 24-hr ABPM and Vasoactive Hormones in Patients With Hypertension.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
